{"tid":2155584,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Cctai 又話唔食藍店又話唔聽藍歌手，但買蘋果股票就用富途牛牛同中銀","createTime":"2020-08-14T01:36:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T12:37:44.000Z","uid":4646,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2de35760015322f457e82e8c8ba86cdf5d239b16","tid":2155584,"uid":4646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T01:36:06.000Z","msg":"壹傳媒 （00282） 創辦人黎智英涉違反「港區國安法」於周一早上被捕後，壹傳媒當日下午起，股價即時爆升。中央結算系統（CCASS）最新更新壹傳媒周一倉位變化，<span class=\"red\">兩大中資中介人、散戶數目龐大的富途證券、中銀香港，為壹傳媒最大淨買入券商</span>，相反美資行盈透（Interactive Brokers）倉位減幅最多。<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒周一起股價、成交大增，當日成交股數已達14.39億股，相當於黎智英持股外的「街貨量」約兩倍，反映股份換手頻密。<br />\n<br />\n富途、中銀香港及安利為三大倉位增加的券商<br />\n<br />\nCCASS數據也顯示，三大倉位增加的券商合計只淨買入5352萬股，相當全日成交股數的3.7%，可見當日投資者進出頻頻，似乎並非單一投資者掃高持貨。<br />\n<br />\n三大倉位增加的券商中，依次為富途證券、中銀香港以及安里證券，倉位分別增加2712萬股、1539萬股和1100萬股，相當於壹傳媒發行股數的1.03%、0.58%及0.42%。<br />\n<br />\n安里證券黃偉康：有客有錢又覺得好炒<br />\n<br />\n安里證券主席兼行政總裁黃偉康稱，有客戶「（自己）有錢又覺得好炒」遂落場買賣，但整體而言未見到當日有太多客戶參與，又指以壹傳媒當日收市價計，該行淨增加的持倉不足300萬元，佔該行整體比例很少。<br />\n<br />\n減持最多的三家券商則分別是盈透、花旗及渣打香港，倉位分別減少2445萬股、993萬股和748萬股，相當於壹傳媒股數的0.93%、0.38%及0.28%。<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒只有8.64億股可供即時交易<br />\n<br />\n值得注意是，壹傳媒只有32.78%發行股數或8.64億股股份在CCASS系統內，可供即時交易。<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒周一、周二股價大幅炒升後，近兩日股價急跌，今日股價全日跌42%，報0.38元，成交2.69億元或5.97億股，換手率依然高企。<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒最新股價較本周即市高位累跌8成，但仍較黎智英被捕前高3倍。"},{"pid":"30eb5b8c4bcada4254b731078c0b0aae6a42f802","tid":2155584,"uid":4646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T01:36:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2723352\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2723352&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBRyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=30474a4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2723352</a>"},{"pid":"2d501f564bdfb2292b4d8fbedb712510b64aea9a","tid":2155584,"uid":4646,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T01:38:08.000Z","msg":"屌人食吉野家 美心就兇狠，自己就用富途牛牛買股票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3bebbee3949ab9aa7d95905bbab09d16d6dd9b","tid":2155584,"uid":23988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T01:38:28.000Z","msg":"富途手續費平，慳埋d錢去食黃店龍門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12ba471119367cfdf283ec075605bb81836cdc05","tid":2155584,"uid":4646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f3bebbee3949ab9aa7d95905bbab09d16d6dd9b","tid":2155584,"uid":23988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T01:38:28.000Z","msg":"富途手續費平，慳埋d錢去食黃店龍門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T01:40:14.000Z","msg":"午餐去金拱門用支那寶慳錢，夜晚去黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c11df946d7a52f3b1230dda17d56544c71a418","tid":2155584,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T01:40:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6cfc230a6009f0597b349e0d29990018777d9012","tid":2155584,"uid":4646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T01:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3247c2df9d45bae016938d80c54b519b8bb198","tid":2155584,"uid":4646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T01:44:22.000Z","msg":"富途牛牛賺錢，藍絲散戶賺錢，今次真係紅色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class